Adds some Piercings for female and male Players/NPC`s

This mod adds 5 Sets of Piercings:
with a total of 62 new Items

for Females: (CBBE-3.1)
Nipple: Rings
Nipple: Sword and Shield
Navel: Barbell in 3 versions
Labia: Rings
All Piercings are available in 2 Editions:
Gold or Silver, with the possibility to add a Gemstone.

for Males: (Bettermales-2.32)
Nipples : Rings
Penis: Rings with PrinceAlbert (erect OR flacid)
All Piercings are available in 2 Editions:
Gold or Silver, with the possibility to add a Gemstone.

All Items can be Crafted, Refined and Enchanted !
..just visit your local Blacksmith (category: Jewelry)
All Piercings work for all Races..!

<--needed for female NipplePiercing (FYI: Labia Piercing should work with any BodyMod)

MALE:
Bettermales - Beautiful nudes and faces VERSION: 2-3-2 --> http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2488 respective the Erect Version
-> Nudes - FavoredSoulMeshes - ErectVersion http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/download/37726
-> Nudes - FavoredSoulMeshes - FlacidVersion http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/download/37731
<-- needed for male GenitalPiercing

PLS USE ONLY 1 OF THE PRINCEALBERT PIERCINGS ! FLACID OR ERECT...
WHEN YOU INSTALL BOTH, THEY DONT CAUSE ANY CRASHES !
BUT THEY SHARE THE SAME INGAME NAMES AND WORLDMODELS,
SO YOU WILL GET 2 SIMILAR ITEMS IN YOUR FORGE, ONLY WHEN YOU EQUIP THEM, YOU CAN SEE THE DIFFERENCE..

NOTICE: for AP users (AnimatedProstitution) in combination with SED7 PrinceAlbert
You can install the flacid base model as standart body
and change the malebody_rude mesh to erect.
but if you will have the rudebody with a Piercing,
you have to do a lil copy/past action in NIFSKOPE to import the Male Piercings.
thisway you will have a pierced standart flacid malebodys and pierced erect when using AP..!
(maybe i create later a lil DLC for this..)

!! the content is best suited with:
Bathing Beauties or Beefcake - Luxury Suite --> http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/11427

Feel free to comment and/or upload Pictures !;)

[img]http://img821.imageshack.us/img821/5894/sed7editionsinstallatio.png[/img]

simply download the files with NMM and activate them..
DONT UPGRADE !! Do just a normal Installation.
IF YOU had a previous version of SED7, confirm if NMM ask you for overwrite !

ALLin1:
The ALLin1 Version contains all editions exept the Penis Piercings !
so you dont need any other files, exept the matching Bodymods (see above)
and additional the erect or flacid Penis Piercing
If you dont like or need one of the included Editions, you can deactivate them
in your NMM or SkyrimLauncher..
OPTIONAL: download SED7 Allin1 Hotfixed1_4 singleESP
NOTE: Hotfixed Single ESP will REMOVE ALL your existing Piercings !! (because of new form ID`s)

STEP BY STEP 4 HOTFIXFILES
How to ALLin1 :
DL the mainfile "SED7-Allin1 Piercingset" (10,486kb size) and install the mod.
go to your Gamefolder "/Data" and delete all SED7 ESPs !!
DL the Hotfix "SED7 Allin1 Hotfixed1_4 singleESP" (6kb size) and install the Hotfix.
make sure that the ESP "SED7-CBBE3-BM_ALLin1-EDITION.esp" is activated...
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
EDITIONS:
You can also download one (or more) of the splitted editions
(exmpl: SED7-CBBE3_GOLDEDITION_femaleNipplePiercing_Rings )
ALL EDITIONS share the same texture files and some Worldmodels (_GO)!!
While the Installation NMM may ask you to overwrite the Textures or _GO.
Just say Yes ! (exept you`ve changed some DDS files manualy)
OPTIONAL: download SED7 Hotfix1_4 esp replacer (replaces ESP`s for all Editions)
NOTE: I created a seperate .esm File for each Edition, so you can enable/disable them independently.

STEP BY STEP4 HOTFIXFILES
How to Optional EDITIONS:
DL one or more optional EDITIONs and install the mods.
DL the Hotfix "SED7 Hotfix1_4 esp replacer" (16kb size) and install the Hotfix.
go to your Gamefolder "/Data" and delete the ESPs you dont need, depending on your optional downloaded EDITIONs..

NOTE !:
I created this mod based on CBBE3 ONLY, never tested with Vanilla or others !!
If you use other bodymods or variants of CBBE i cant guarantee if they work !!

FYI: (shortfix)
sometimes it may happens that your Players weight isnt setback to your choosen setting.
this happens mostly when you equip armors/clothes which are based on other bodymods than you use. (EXPL: use CBBE and wear BBP)
to fix this: simply open console, type showracemenu, and move the weight slider a lil bit. then you should notice that it shows correct now..

1ST What you can do is; READ the description EDITION AND INSTALLATION !!!!!
--> redownload the mod and Install NORMAL ! DONT UPDATE !
2ND check if you have all files in your datafolder.. check the readme for this !
(you find the latest Readme always here, (scroll up, click readme))
3TH i never noticed problems with other mods, but try to load your game with ONLY SED7 activated, and ofcourse the matching bodymods..
4TH PLS make SURE that you have tryed the above steps !
